reviews.review_text:
ah, memories this was a mind bending show. 
i was a Ventura boy, so all these runs were special for me, but this show. 
Phil. 
thank you Hunter for this gorgeous production.
LOSER You'll never find a better version of Loser. The gritty growl after the solo is something you dont hear very often.
